author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week on the podcast, we’re doing something a little different. We’re gearing up for the premiere of Marvel Studios’ Fantastic Four: First Steps by exploring the history and impact of Marvel’s First Family through a discussion driven by those who know them best! Tune in as a quartet of Fantastic Four comic book writers– Jonathan Hickman, Ryan North, Mark Waid, and Chip Zdarsky-- break down just what makes the FF so special.
